assignRole(uint256,address,uint8).details: Only contract owner can use this function

confirmTransfer(uint256).details: Called by new owner to confirm receipt

params.productId: ID of the product being confirmed

returns._0: Array of addresses who previously owned the product

getRoleString(uint256,address).details: Converts internal enum to string for UI use

returns._0: The role as a string ("Supplier", "Manufacturer", etc.)

logManufacturing(uint256,string).details: Used by the manufacturer to log actions taken on the product

logMaterialInput(uint256,string,string).details: Only the product's current owner (typically the supplier) can log

registerProduct().details: Everyone can register a raw material product, and considered as Supplier for that product

returns._0: productId Unique ID assigned to the product

verifyMaterialQuality(uint256,string).details: Manufacturer must be the current owner
